<section id="philosophy" class="mt-32 relative reveal">

    <!-- Background decorative shapes -->
    <div class="absolute inset-0 -z-10 opacity-20 pointer-events-none">
        <div class="absolute top-10 left-20 w-40 h-40 bg-blue-600 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-10 right-20 w-40 h-40 bg-yellow-500 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    </div>

    <!-- Title -->
    <h2 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-center mb-10">
        The Philosophy of <span class="text-blue-600 dark:text-yellow-400">Tarazism</span>
    </h2>

    <!-- Manifesto text -->
    <p class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center text-lg text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 leading-relaxed mb-16">
        <strong>Taraz</strong> (تَراز) is the pursuit of balance — harmonious expression,
        refined craftsmanship, depth without excess, meaning without noise.
        <br /><br />
        Tarazism is a lens: a way of evaluating art, media, and stories not by popularity,
        but by how they resonate with equilibrium, attention, and beauty.
    </p>

    <!-- Accordion of Concepts -->
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">

        <div id="accordion-philosophy" data-accordion="collapse">

            <!-- Concept 1 -->
            <h2 id="heading-balance">
                <button type="button"
                        class="flex justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left"
                        data-accordion-target="#concept-balance" aria-expanded="true" aria-controls="concept-balance">
                    <span>⚖ Balance (تَوازُن)</span>
                    <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-6 h-6 rotate-180 shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                              d="M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 10.94l3.71-3.71a.75.75 0 111.08 1.04l-4.25 4.25a.75.75 0 01-1.08 0L5.21 8.27a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06z"
                              clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="concept-balance" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="heading-balance">
                <div class="p-5 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    True balance is not neutrality — it is the interplay of forces that elevate each other.
                    In art, balance manifests through pacing, aesthetics, themes, emotional weight.
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Concept 2 -->
            <h2 id="heading-depth">
                <button type="button"
                        class="flex justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left"
                        data-accordion-target="#concept-depth" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="concept-depth">
                    <span>🌒 Depth without Excess</span>
                    <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                              d="M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 10.94l3.71-3.71a.75.75 0 111.08 1.04l-4.25 4.25a.75.75 0 01-1.08 0L5.21 8.27a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06z"
                              clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="concept-depth" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="heading-depth">
                <div class="p-5 border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                    Tarazism favors works that explore complexity with clarity — not noise.
                    Depth comes from intention, not confusion.
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Concept 3 -->
            <h2 id="heading-craft">
                <button type="button"
                        class="flex justify-between w-full p-5 font-medium border-b border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700 text-left"
                        data-accordion-target="#concept-craft" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="concept-craft">
                    <span>🛠 Refined Craftsmanship</span>
                    <svg data-accordion-icon class="w-6 h-6 shrink-0" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20">
                        <path fill-rule="evenodd"
                              d="M5.23 7.21a.75.75 0 011.06.02L10 10.94l3.71-3.71a.75.75 0 111.08 1.04l-4.25 4.25a.75.75 0 01-1.08 0L5.21 8.27a.75.75 0 01.02-1.06z"
                              clip-rule="evenodd" />
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </h2>
            <div id="concept-craft" class="hidden" aria-labelledby="heading-craft">
                <div class="p-5">
                    Every detail matters — composition, writing, animation, sound, pacing.
                    Tarazism rewards craft that reveals effort and care.
                </div>
            </div>

        </div>

    </div>

</section>
